These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
House: ranch-style, cottage, townhouse
There 3 different types of food: lemon, plum, spinach
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, thriller, fantasy
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, snowmobile, car
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, august, october
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, vegafina, havana
 1. the swisher-smoker is the german##1
 2. the havana-smoker is the person driving the car##1
 3. the townhouse house is between the italian and the cottage house##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is the colombian##1
 7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 8. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 9. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| House      | cottage    | townhouse   | ranch-style           |
| Food          | plum       | spinach    | lemon         |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller    | fantasy  | adventure        |
| Transport           | ship | snowmobile   | car      |
| Birthday   | august        | october    | september       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| Cigar         | swisher     | vegafina | havana |

