3 different games are played: billiard, snooker, poker
City: edinburgh, rome, prague
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, iris, zinnia
House: modern, cape-cod, wooden
 1. the person who growszinnia is the person traveling to rome##1
 2. the person who growszinnia is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 4. the modern house is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
 5. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person playing billiard##1
 7. the person playing snooker is on the left of the wooden house##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person playing poker##1
10. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Hobby      | dancing   | card-games    | traveling         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | disaster  | animation     |
