.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, whist, go
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, august, april
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade, juice
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, azalea, bellflower
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, indian, russian
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, coach, chef
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, swimming
 1. the person playing whist is the coach##1
 2. the russian is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is the person playing go##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is the coach##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is between the indian and the person who growsbellflower##2
 8. the indian is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 9. the coach is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the chef is on the right of the person playing whist##1
11. the indian is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Game          | go      | whist      | monopoly      |
| Birthday         | september   | april | august |
| Beverage   | mirinda | lemonade    | juice          |
| Flower   | azalea       | iris      | bellflower          |
| Nationality   | indian    | egyptian  | russian      |
| Job           | doctor   | coach  | chef        |
| Sport         | climbing  | sailing   | swimming     |

