.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-17::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, tea
House: ranch-style, farmhouse, colonial
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, december, january
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, blue, ivory
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, guinea-pig
3 different games are played: scrabble, domino, snooker
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, begonia, daisy
 1. the person playing snooker is in the middle##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 4. the colonial house is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 7. the person who growsdaisy is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who likes pink##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | tea      |
| House         | ranch-style     | farmhouse     | colonial  |
| Birthday   | january | february  | december |
| Color   | blue  | ivory     | pink |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Game         | scrabble    | snooker | domino   |
| Flower     | begonia        | daisy        | balloon-flower   |

