.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, tulip, amaryllis
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, october, february
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, pall-mall, chaman
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, manager, musician
3 different games are played: chess, backgammon, billiard
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, water-polo
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, snake, pony
1. the person who growstulip is on the left of the musician##1
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the dressmaker##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person playing chess and the manager##2
5. the person who's birthday is in february is between the musician and the chaman-smoker##2
6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
9. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Flower      | zinnia      | tulip      | amaryllis       |
| Birthday          | october      | february    | september   |
| Cigar         | chaman    | dunhill     | pall-mall     |
| Job           | manager    | dressmaker | musician   |
| Game   | backgammon    | billiard    | chess       |
| Sport         | water-polo | rugby      | surfing    |
| Pet     | snake       | chinchilla | pony |

