.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, alhambra, dunhill
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, dahlia, begonia
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, thai, japanese
3 different pets are kept: turtle, chinchilla, dog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, snowboarding
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, lavender, brown
1. the person who likes lavender is the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the polish##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the japanese is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is between the person drinking fanta and the person who growsdaisy##2
6. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
8. the person who likes blue is the japanese##1
9. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | fanta       | coffee     | cola         |
| Cigar          | bluemaster     | alhambra      | dunhill     |
| Flower         | dahlia | begonia    | daisy      |
| Nationality   | polish   | thai | japanese    |
| Pet   | chinchilla        | dog     | turtle   |
| Sport         | cricket     | ice-hockey | snowboarding |
| Color     | lavender     | brown       | blue    |

