.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, photography, fishing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, satire, epic
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, fisherman, nurse
House: art-deco, cottage, tower
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, punk, funk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, old-henry, davidoff
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person driving the roller is the baccarat-smoker##1
3. the dressmaker is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the fan of funk##2
4. the art-deco house is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the fan of indie is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the fisherman is the person watching horror movies##1
8. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of indie##1
9. the cottage house is between the person watching horror movies and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby      | photography    | drawing       | fishing      |
| Movie-Genre          | horror   | epic   | satire  |
| Job           | fisherman  | dressmaker | nurse    |
| House   | art-deco   | cottage     | tower  |
| Music-Genre           | funk     | indie        | punk |
| Cigar         | old-henry | baccarat   | davidoff  |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | roller     | car      |

 